                    "body": "I created jekyll-jupyter-notebook gem because it'll be useful not only Apache Arrow site but also other sites.\n\nUsage:\n\n{noformat}\n{::nomarkdown}\n{% jupyter_notebook getting_started.ipynb %}\n{:/nomarkdown}\n{noformat}\n\n\nCSS related problems may be caused but there is no problem case yet. (We don't use the plugin yet.)\nHow about considering about the problems when we get the problems?",
